'''葛林兄弟'''（{{lang-en|Green brothers}}）是指'''[[約翰·葛林|約翰·葛林]]'''（{{lang|en|John Green}}；1977年8月24日－）和'''{{le|漢克·葛林|Hank Green}}'''（{{lang|en|Hank Green}}；1980年5月5日－）兩兄弟。他們兩人是美國企業家、{{le|互聯網活動人士|Internet activism}}和YouTube[[VLOG|影片博主]]。兩兄弟在兩人的事業和生活中都有頗大影響，因2007年開始「兄弟情 2.0」（{{lang|en|Brotherhood 2.0}}）而開始受歡迎。兩人在YouTube上有約15條頻道，包括主頻道{{le|VlogBrothers|VlogBrothers}}、{{le|SciShow|SciShow}}和{{le|The Lizzie Bennet Diaries|The Lizzie Bennet Diaries}}<ref>{{cite web|last=Green|first=Hank|authorlink=Hank Green|url=https://medium.com/@hankgreen/do-other-peoples-youtube-cpms-look-this-good-f92db1fa71eb|title=Do Other People's YouTube CPMs Look This Good?|publisher=''Medium''|date=October 5, 2014|accessdate=October 7, 2014|archive-date=2020-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923171858/https://medium.com/@hankgreen/do-other-peoples-youtube-cpms-look-this-good-f92db1fa71eb|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Browning|first=Skylar|url=http://missoulanews.bigskypress.com/IndyBlog/archives/2013/08/26/missoulas-hank-green-wins-an-emmy|title=Missoula's Hank Green wins an Emmy|publisher=''Big Sky Press''|work=Missoula Independent|date=August 26, 2013|accessdate=October 7, 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140821143407/http://missoulanews.bigskypress.com/IndyBlog/archives/2013/08/26/missoulas-hank-green-wins-an-emmy|archivedate=2014年8月21日}}</ref>。

[[約翰·葛林|約翰·葛林]]因為他的小說《[[生命中的美好缺憾|生命中的美好缺憾]]》和[[生命中的美好缺憾_(電影)|其改編電影]]由YouTube名人變成荷里活名星。雖然小說在[[紐約時報暢銷書榜|紐約時報暢銷書榜]]排行第一和電影票房成績良好，約翰仍認為他是因為例如[[Crash_Course|Crash Course]]的網上項目而知名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/best-sellers-books/2012-01-29/chapter-books/list.html|title=Best Sellers – Children's Chapter Books|publisher=''The New York Times''|date=January 29, 2012|accessdate=October 7, 2014|archive-date=2012-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120124030531/http://www.nytimes.com/best-sellers-books/2012-01-29/chapter-books/list.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=WSJsummerblockbuster>{{cite web|last=Alter|first=Alexandra|url=http://online.wsj.com/articles/john-green-and-his-nerdfighters-are-upending-the-summer-blockbuster-model-1400088712?tesla=y&mg=reno64-wsj&url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052702304431104579552173066169420.html|title=John Green and His Nerdfighters Are Upending the Summer Blockbuster Model|publisher=''The Wall Street Journal''|date=May 14, 2014|accessdate=October 7, 2014|archive-date=2014-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140614121216/http://online.wsj.com/articles/john-green-and-his-nerdfighters-are-upending-the-summer-blockbuster-model-1400088712?tesla=y&mg=reno64-wsj&url=http%3A%2F%2Fonline.wsj.com%2Farticle%2FSB10001424052702304431104579552173066169420.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

{{le|漢克·葛林|Hank Green}}則自己知名，創立了環保為題的網誌「EcoGeek」。該網誌原為他在[[蒙大拿大學|蒙大拿大學]]修讀時的學生專案，但是漸漸成為了一個主要的環保資訊網，後來《[[時代_(雜誌)|時代]]》雜誌亦有報導<ref>{{cite web|last=Weber|first=Jonathan|url=http://newwest.net/main/article/ecogeek_makes_a_splash_in_debut/|title=EcoGeek Makes a Splash in Debut|publisher=''New West''|date=April 11, 2006|accessdate=October 7, 2014|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807153035/https://newwest.net/main/article/ecogeek_makes_a_splash_in_debut/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Roston|first=Eric|url=http://content.time.com/time/specials/2007/article/0,28804,1730759_1731034_1731054,00.html|title=EcoGeek|publisher=''Time''|date=April 17, 2008|accessdate=October 7, 2014|archive-date=2016-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160916234628/http://content.time.com/time/specials/2007/article/0,28804,1730759_1731034_1731054,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。漢克亦因為共同創辦唱片公司{{le|DFTBA Records|DFTBA Records}}獲得知名度<ref name=ChicagoTribuneDFTBArecords>{{cite web|last=RedEye|first=Stephanie Lulay|url=http://online.wsj.com/articles/john-green-and-his-nerdfighters-are-upending-the-summer-blockbuster-model-1400088712?tesla=y&mg=reno64-wsj&url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2009-12-07/news/0912070155_1_music-label-youtube-band|title=I'm with the bandwidth|publisher=''Chicago Tribune''|date=December 7, 2009|accessdate=October 7, 2014}}</ref>。

兩人一同創造的內容網絡被稱為「網上多媒體帝國」（{{lang|en|online multimedia empire}}）<ref name=WSJsummerblockbuster/><ref name=NYTimesCarnegie>{{cite web|last=Kaufman|first=Leslie|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/01/17/books/john-and-hank-green-bring-their-show-to-carnegie-hall.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0|title=A Novelist and His Brother Sell Out Carnegie Hall|publisher=''The New York Times''|date=January 16, 2013|accessdate=October 7, 2014|archive-date=2019-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191211225043/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/01/17/books/john-and-hank-green-bring-their-show-to-carnegie-hall.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=WTSuccessStory>{{cite web|last=Lindquist|first=David|url=http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2014/sep/26/greens-success-born-of-lessons-learned-hard-way/?page=all|title=Green's success born of lessons learned hard way|publisher=''Washington Times''|date=September 26, 2014|accessdate=October 7, 2014|archive-date=2016-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160124165910/http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2014/sep/26/greens-success-born-of-lessons-learned-hard-way/?page=all|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。該網絡的內容種類包括教育、遊戲、生活等，而他們兩人的[[迷文化|粉都]]叫作「{{le|Nerdfighteria|Nerdfighteria}}」<ref name=NYTimesCarnegie/><ref>{{cite web|last=Romano|first=Aja|url=http://www.dailydot.com/society/hank-john-green-vlogborthers-nerdfighters/|title=DFTBA: Behind the Vlogbrothers' Nerdfighters movement|publisher=''The Daily Dot''|date=August 20, 2012|accessdate=October 21, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210306072223/https://www.dailydot.com/society/hank-john-green-vlogborthers-nerdfighters/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

